# Copy to `.env.local` (git-ignored by Vite) to point the game at a real backend.
#
# Unset (the default, and on GitHub Pages) → the in-browser MockBackend is used and the game stays a
# fully static site. Set this to a Node service that implements src/backend/README.md and the identical
# game code talks to it via HttpBackend — no other changes needed.
#
# VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://api.example.com
